<section style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
  <h2>Why People Are Buying Dyson Airwrap Complete</h2>
  <p>Many people damage their hair with high-heat styling tools like flat irons and curling wands. Traditional blow dryers require skill to achieve a polished look, and salon visits are expensive. The Dyson Airwrap became popular because it promises professional results with less heat damage at home.</p>
