<!-- 3. SOLUTION -->
<section style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
  <h2>What Is Dyson Airwrap Complete?</h2>
  <p>The Dyson Airwrap is a multi-attachment styling tool that uses the Coanda effect — high-velocity airflow that attracts and wraps hair around the barrel. It comes with barrels for curling, brushes for smoothing, and a dryer attachment. It went viral when beauty influencers demonstrated effortless curls without clamping or burning.</p>
  <p style="margin-top:1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;">
    <span style="font-size:.75rem;font-family:var(--font-sans);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--muted-foreground);">Why it went viral:</span>
    <span style="color:var(--accent);font-size:.875rem;">Beauty TikTok showing effortless salon curls at home</span>
  </p>
</section>

<div class="divider-gradient" style="margin-bottom:3rem;"></div>

<!-- 4. HOW TO USE -->
<section style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
  <h2>How to Use Dyson Airwrap Complete</h2>
  <ol class="how-to-steps">
    <li class="how-to-step"><span class="step-number">1</span><span class="step-text">Start with damp, towel-dried hair — the Airwrap works best on wet-to-dry styling</span></li>
    <li class="how-to-step"><span class="step-number">2</span><span class="step-text">Select the appropriate attachment for your desired style (barrels for curls, brushes for volume)</span></li>
    <li class="how-to-step"><span class="step-number">3</span><span class="step-text">Hold sections of hair near the barrel and let the Coanda effect wrap the hair automatically</span></li>
    <li class="how-to-step"><span class="step-number">4</span><span class="step-text">Style each section for 10–15 seconds, then switch to cool shot to set the curl</span></li>
  </ol>
</section>

